{"ID":"20260609132344-rf5q5aw","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609132344-rf5q5aw","title":"2021年浙江卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609132725"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609132408-v2tp4qr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132408-v2tp4qr","updated":"20260609132408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．下列各句中，没有错别字且加点字的注音全都正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132408-guko7yc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132408-guko7yc","updated":"20260609132408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．各种春菜在田间地垄悄然探出头，娇弱的身子轻轻摇曳（yì），而稚嫩的豌豆尖更是惹人喜爱，叶子清澈通透如翡翠薄片，茎上嫩须迎风轻颤（chàn），引逗着人们去采撷。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132408-wbg8td7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132408-wbg8td7","updated":"20260609132408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．创新型国家建设不是一蹴（cù）而就的，需要科技工作者心无旁骛，摒（bǐng）弃拜金主义，以甘为人梯，奖掖后学的精神，帮助青少年成为科学研究和技术攻坚的人才。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132408-ze88mqx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132408-ze88mqx","updated":"20260609132408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．《典籍里的中国》用追根溯源、旁证博引的方式驰骋（chěng）上下五千年，从文明的起源讲到现代传承，让观众眼界大开，堪称当下文化节目的扛（gāng）鼎之作。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132408-e1vmcir","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132408-e1vmcir","updated":"20260609132408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．那些或坐落于安静的小镇古街、或藏身在喧嚣的商业密林的个性实体书店，在充满竞争的时代执拗（niù）生长，规模不大却洋溢着审美情趣，足以让灵魂片刻栖（qī）身。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-fp0twyc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-fp0twyc","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阅读下面的文字，完成下面小题。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-vbts3ar","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-vbts3ar","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"【甲】中国传统工艺设计注重“材美”“工巧”“器雅”，古人对于器物的形状、质地、色彩的追求可谓"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"孜孜不倦"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一件器物，可以拙朴到浑然天成，不露声色，也可以繁复，精美到无以复加。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"【乙】“过去的生活，一切都很慢”，因此无论是天潢贵胄，还是黎民百姓，家里"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"或许"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"都会有几件称心如意的工艺品，点缀他们的“慢生活”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-6kbvt7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-6kbvt7k","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在经济高速发展的今天，那些与生活息息相关、具有温度的传统工艺家具与器物，除了留存在一些宫殿、宅第、民居中，还在热衷传统工艺设计的美术家手中不断传承。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"【丙】家具、器物、雅玩里不仅仅蕴藏着中国传统工艺源远流长且不断革新的丰富技法；更折射出中国人对幸福生活的虔诚态度。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-5717ygb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-5717ygb","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．文段中的加点词语，运用不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-exzeo9f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-exzeo9f","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．孜孜不倦                    B．不露声色                    C．或许                              D．留存"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-crsnyn2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-crsnyn2","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．文段中画线的甲、乙、丙句，标点有误的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132445-l289x3g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132445-l289x3g","updated":"20260609132445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．甲                                                  B．乙                                                 C．丙"}]},{"ID":"20260609132551-4x681ui","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132551-4x681ui","updated":"20260609132551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4．下列各句中，没有语病的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132551-7a55x8c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132551-7a55x8c","updated":"20260609132551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．一些平台正通过减少不必要的中间环节，提升整个农产品供应链的效率，用户不但能享受到更低价格和更新鲜的农产品，还能促进农民增收以及通过再投资改善生产。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132551-9dp51nf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132551-9dp51nf","updated":"20260609132551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．文化产业高质量发展必须自觉承担起调动各种文化力量，科技力量和市场力量，为中华民族的伟大复兴、为人民所向往的美好生活，为中国价值更受世人尊重而砥砺前行。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132551-b4m4rkm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132551-b4m4rkm","updated":"20260609132551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．近期，公安部联合主要媒体网站持续推出反诈骗系列报道，不断加强社会宣传，扩大宣传精准性，构建立足社区、覆盖全社会的宣传体系，掀起全社会共同反诈骗的热潮。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132551-qvvkgh2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132551-qvvkgh2","updated":"20260609132551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．推进乡村振兴工作应该抓好人才队伍建设，加大力度培育新型职业农民，制定吸引人才、留住人才的政策措施，鼓励大学生、城市在职科技人员、退休人员积极参与。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132652-zhjvvde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132652-zhjvvde","updated":"20260609132652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5．下列各句中，表达不得体的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132652-l0abbn9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132652-l0abbn9","updated":"20260609132652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．使用公筷广告：长筷短筷，筷筷都是你我的爱。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132652-44kk8h0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132652-44kk8h0","updated":"20260609132652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．论文答辩致谢语：感谢聆听，敬请专家评委指教。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132652-92k2eol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132652-92k2eol","updated":"20260609132652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．垃圾分类宣传语：各得其所，细微处的文明之光。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132652-ye7iyb1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132652-ye7iyb1","updated":"20260609132652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．经典阅读推荐：智慧火源，值得为之付出热忱。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132344-zuwrebi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132344-zuwrebi","updated":"20260609132707"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609132344-w3u1dwp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132344-w3u1dwp","updated":"20260609132707"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．D   2．B    3．C    4．D    5．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609132344-i2iqo0k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132344-i2iqo0k","updated":"20260609132725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609132509-8oq4p0t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132509-8oq4p0t","updated":"20260609132539"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．本题考查学生识记现代汉语常用字字音、字形的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132510-egaf8s7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132510-egaf8s7","updated":"20260609132510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“摇曳”的“曳”读音错误，应为“yè”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132510-sm73wjb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132510-sm73wjb","updated":"20260609132510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“摒弃”的“摒”读音错误，应为“bìng”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132510-pxoexi5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132510-pxoexi5","updated":"20260609132510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“旁证博引”的“证”字形错误，应为“征”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132510-9u21jw8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132510-9u21jw8","updated":"20260609132510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-ub8mvnq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-ub8mvnq","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．本题考查学生正确使用词语（包括熟语）的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-xohqtei","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-xohqtei","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.孜孜不倦：指工作或学习勤奋不知疲倦。本处指古人对于器物的形状、质地、色彩的追求不知疲倦，所以运用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-xmkawqe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-xmkawqe","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.不露声色：心里的打算不在说话和脸色上显露出来。这里的陈述对象是器物，是说器物的拙朴，而不是指人，所以不露声色运用错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-4daviik","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-4daviik","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.或许：也许，不一定的意思。这里是指无论是天潢贵胄还是黎民百姓家里也许都会有几件称心如意的工艺品，所以运用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-6s2i9gu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-6s2i9gu","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.留存：存留、保存。本处指那些传统工艺家具与器物除了保存在一些宫殿、宅第、民居中，还在热衷传统工艺设计的美术家手中不断传承，所以运用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-2h1v73r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-2h1v73r","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-thwmxzw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-thwmxzw","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．本题考查学生正确使用标点符号的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-ofztp00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-ofztp00","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“分号”运用错误。“不仅仅……更”表示递进关系，并非两个并列句子，中间的“分号”应该改为“逗号”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132523-llrms98","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132523-llrms98","updated":"20260609132523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132627-5hrt5fj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132627-5hrt5fj","updated":"20260609132636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132624-y271oqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132624-y271oqp","updated":"20260609132624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“用户不但能享受到更低价格和更新鲜的农产品”错误。首先，“不但”语序不当，应将“不但”放到“用户”前面；其次，在“用户”前面加上“使”，否则导致中途易辙。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132624-cdoe0a3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132624-cdoe0a3","updated":"20260609132624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.句中“承担”缺少宾语中心语，应在最后加上“的重任”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132624-4ztvq1b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132624-4ztvq1b","updated":"20260609132624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“扩大宣传精准性”中，“扩大”和“精准性”搭配不当，可将“扩大”改为“提高”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132624-sp50cia","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132624-sp50cia","updated":"20260609132624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132719-9qkw9va","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132719-9qkw9va","updated":"20260609132725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5．本题考查学生语言表达得体的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132719-fu1tclx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132719-fu1tclx","updated":"20260609132719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“聆听”表达不得体。聆听是指集中精力认真地听。指虔诚而认真地听取，带有尊重被听者的色彩。而且，这个词一般由听讲者使用。而语境是指专家和评委听自己的论文答辩，使用错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132719-z59ea5t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132719-z59ea5t","updated":"20260609132719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}